{"tid":1066804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會俾人話似某一個明星（秒經）","createTime":"2019-03-18T06:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:21:59.000Z","uid":71949,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2bce59aa6a17b56cdd9693d032b9f7608d782896","tid":1066804,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友係唔同時期成日比D人話過佢個樣似好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同期<br />\n<br />\n18~22似吳尊,洪卓立/<br />\n23~24似吳唱K,炎亞綸,林峰<br />\n25~26似劉鎧威(整容後),霍建華,林德信,小豬<br />\n27~28又似返吳唱K,吳尊,許廷鏗,甚至 大陸明星 俞灝明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最大獲係就嚟三十歲條友成日比女仔話似姜濤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過條友著衫好求其都係t卹牛仔褲咁. <br />\n<br />\n完全唔知呢班人有咩共通點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n我朋友唔係我,<br />\n我比人話似孔慶翔,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阮兆祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad9c33359d890f3c82a277a2202cce0b27041d5","tid":1066804,"uid":75754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"陳坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca40f71a2f2328c49bce2072444fe35d9c051d19","tid":1066804,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b8af474af333a18cbb4418461e8a1a4006b0f0e","tid":1066804,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aad9c33359d890f3c82a277a2202cce0b27041d5","tid":1066804,"uid":75754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"陳坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1799b8850e599a43de384088d9a72725611cce5","tid":1066804,"uid":